Interface UtilizationModel

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    UtilizationModelFull, UtilizationModelNull, UtilizationModelPlanetLabInMemory, UtilizationModelStochastic

    public interface UtilizationModel
    The UtilizationModel interface needs to be implemented in order to provide a fine-grained control over resource usage by a Cloudlet.
